---
// ChainOfCustody.astro
// EL GRAN DIFERENCIADOR: ningún competidor chileno muestra qué pasa con el dispositivo
// después del retiro. Esta sección llena ese vacío con transparencia radical.
---

<section id="cadena" class="section-padding" style="background-color: #0B1B32;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <!-- Differentiator callout -->
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border mb-5"
        style="border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.35); background: rgba(185,115,51,0.08);"
      >
        <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" style="color:#B97333;">
          <path d="M10 12a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"/>
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M.458 10C1.732 5.943 5.522 3 10 3s8.268 2.943 9.542 7c-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7S1.732 14.057.458 10zM14 10a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase" style="color:#B97333;" data-i18n="chain.badge">
          Transparencia total: lo que nadie más te muestra
        </span>
      </div>

      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        data-i18n="chain.title"
      >Tu equipo llega aquí.<br/>Esto pasa después.</h2>
      <p
        class="text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        style="color: #8E9297;"
        data-i18n="chain.subtitle"
      >
        Mientras otros te entregan un certificado al final, nosotros te mostramos
        cada paso del recorrido. Control total de principio a fin.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Chain of Custody — 6 steps grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">

      <!-- Step 1 — Retiro en tu empresa -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-1 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"
        >
          <!-- Step number -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
            >01</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.0.title">
            Retiro en tus instalaciones
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.0.desc">
            Coordinamos el retiro en tu empresa con flota certificada, manifiestos de transporte y acta de recepción firmada. Tú recibes confirmación inmediata.
          </p>
          <!-- Status tag -->
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.0.tag">Acta de recepción emitida</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 — Recepción y pesaje -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-2 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
            >02</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.1.title">
            Recepción y pesaje certificado
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.1.desc">
            Cada RAEE es pesado, fotografiado e ingresado a nuestro sistema de trazabilidad con número de serie único. Recibes reporte de ingreso dentro de 24 horas.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.1.tag">Reporte de ingreso en 24h</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 — Destrucción de datos -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-3 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.07); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
        >
          <!-- FEATURED: Data destruction — trigger principal de decisión corporativa -->
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.2); color: #B97333;">
              Crítico
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.25); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.5);"
            >03</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.2);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.2.title">
            Destrucción certificada de datos
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.2.desc">
            Borrado seguro o destrucción física del soporte de almacenamiento. Certificado individual por dispositivo con número de serie, método y fecha, válido para auditorías de cumplimiento normativo.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.2.tag">Certificado por dispositivo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 — Desmantelamiento y clasificación -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-2 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
            >04</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.3.title">
            Desmantelamiento y clasificación
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.3.desc">
            Separación manual y mecánica de componentes: metales ferrosos, cobre, aluminio, tarjetas electrónicas, plásticos y materiales peligrosos. Protocolo certificado por SEREMI de Salud.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.3.tag">Protocolo SEREMI autorizado</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 — Valorización de materiales -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-3 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
            >05</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.4.title">
            Valorización de materiales
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.4.desc">
            Recuperación de cobre, oro, plata, paladio, aluminio y plásticos de ingeniería. Los materiales regresan al ciclo productivo como materia prima secundaria.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.4.tag">Materiales regresan al ciclo productivo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 6 — Certificado de disposición final -->
      <div class="reveal stagger-4 group">
        <div
          class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 h-full border transition-all duration-300"
          style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-black"
              style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15); color: #B97333; border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
            >06</div>
            <div class="flex-1 h-px" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.15);"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" fill="none" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n="chain.steps.5.title">
            Certificado en tu correo
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.steps.5.desc">
            Certificado digital de disposición final, reporte de materiales recuperados y métricas de impacto ambiental (CO₂ evitado, kg valorizados). Listo para tu reporte ESG o auditoría REP.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.8);">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 inline-block"></span>
            <span data-i18n="chain.steps.5.tag">Válido para reporte ESG y REP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA row -->
    <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(185,115,51,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(185,115,51,0.2);">
      <div>
        <p class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-1" data-i18n="chain.cta.title">
          ¿Listo para ver el proceso en acción?
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #8E9297;" data-i18n="chain.cta.subtitle">
          Agenda tu primera recolección y recibe tu certificado dentro de 5 días hábiles.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl whitespace-nowrap"
        style="background-color: #B97333; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(185,115,51,0.3);"
        data-i18n="chain.cta.button"
      >
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
        Agenda tu retiro
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
